text: One FM is a Malaysian Chinese-language radio station. Initially starting with broadcasts in the Klang Valley, it is now broadcast nationwide. One FM is owned by Media Prima Berhad. ==DJs== ===Morning Kaki=== * Angeline * Nicholas * 丁丁 ===10-4 with Hana=== * Hana ===Happy Hour=== * William ===Happy Dedication=== * Dino ===Weekend DJ=== * Angel 迎晶 * Gigi * Chrystina ===News broadcaster=== * Gigi * Bryan * Vicky ==Frequency== {| class="wikitable" !
